      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model and contact formulation appropriate for titanium alloy elastic-plastic behavior under quasi-static bending; documented justification.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening (BISO) constitutive model applied to Ti-6Al-4V rod and screw. Augmented Lagrange contact at screw-rod and screw-block interfaces. Model form justified by comparison to published titanium alloy characterization data and prior FDA pedicle screw FEA studies."
    },
