      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometry sourced from traceable measurements or certified material data sheets; uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (1.1 GPa) taken from ASTM B265 certified mill certificates for the specific lot used in testing. Geometric dimensions measured via CMM on representative samples. Input uncertainty propagated via ±5% material property perturbation study."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
