      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Eq. 5-1 for stiffness (1.41), yield force (1.38), and force at 40 mm displacement (0.97). All three QoIs satisfy the E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion. Percentage differences also within the pre-specified 10% bound."
    },
    {
