      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in the COU and directly correspond to the mechanical performance endpoints required by FDA guidance for pedicle screw systems. Clinical relevance established through linkage to fatigue failure initiation at yield."
